    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Emacs: Статический анализ Ruby-кода]]></title>
    <link href="http://sviridov.github.io/blog/2014/06/28/emacs-ruby-static-code-analysis/"/>
    <updated>2014-06-28T14:22:10+06:00</updated>
